## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/intrinsic">Intrinsic</a> matches are combinations of <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a> matchers, and argument matchers.

Higher arity matcher are defined recursively in terms of and-ing them with lower arity matchers. Here&#39;s some convenient typedefs for up to several arguments, and more can be added as needed
